<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>For My Love ❤️</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            max-width: 350px;
        }

        img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ff4b5c;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .heart {
            font-size: 30px;
            animation: beat 1s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes beat {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.2); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="card">
        <!-- Replace the image URL with your girlfriend's picture -->
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="My Love">

        <h1>Hi Baby ❤️</h1>
        <p>
            I just want you to know that you make my world brighter every day.
            Thank you for loving me, supporting me, and being my happiness.
        </p>

        <p class="heart">❤️</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
